for my bigger-sized butt, I find the smaller chair&nbsp;
to be slightly more comfortable. But the thing is,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:14.000 --> 00:07:19.440
while we really enjoyed these over the years,&nbsp;
we're not sure where it fits in our home today.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:19.440 --> 00:07:25.280
For work, we no longer sit on floor chairs with&nbsp;
